Fragments
-


FRAGMENT LIFECYCLE

onAttach - Fragment attached to activity.
onCreate - Fragment initialisation part.
onCreateView - Fragment View initialisation part.
onViewCreated - View is created.
onStart - View becoming visible to user.
onResume - View completely visible to user, they can interact.
onPause - Partially visible, user can not interact
onStop - Invisible, user cannot interact.
onDestroyView - View destroyed.
onDestroy - Fragment destroyed
onDetach - Fragment removed from Activity
